   :description => "Halflings are an affable and cheerful people. They cherish the bonds of family and friendship as well as the comforts of hearth and home, harboring few dreams of gold or glory. Even adventurers among them usually venture into the world for reasons of community, friendship, wanderlust, or curiosity. They lave discovering new things, even simple things, such as an exotic food or an unfamiliar style of c1othing.",
